# Cosmic Ocean: World Layout Blueprint (V1)

*This document serves as the absolute source of truth for the spatial layout of Cosmic Ocean. It converts the conceptual regions from the GDD and the architecture limits from the TAD into an exact, buildable coordinate system.*

---

